cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.MM, cs.GT 

This paper deals with optimization of resource allocation and user association in wireless networks, which is a common topic in the field of network information theory (cs.IT) and network optimization (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the non-convex optimization problem, which is a common challenge in control systems (cs.SY). The use of closed-form solutions and numerical results suggest that the paper may also be relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) and game theory (cs.GT) sub-categories.
